title: Real Love Don't Need Prenups
itunes:title: Real Love Don't Need Prenups
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines for our married listeners to see if they got a prenup or not after many wanted Brittney Spears to get a prenup after her recenet engagement. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a Maryland man who was sentenced to 10 years for attacking woman with a semen filled syringe! Also, we opened up the phone lines to see what our listener thought of the woman who fought off a robber at her subway job but then ended up getting suspended for it.
